origin_airport.description: The origin airport to search from.

destination_airport.description: The destination airport to search to.

departure_date.description: Departure date to search, in YYYY-MM-DD format.

source.description: The mileage program to search. Can be one of: [united, delta, virginatlantic, velocity, aeroplan, alaska]

disable_filters.description: Disables any filters for dynamic pricing or mismatched airports.

get.description: Retrieve a large amount of availability objects from one specific mileage program.

parameters.name: source
parameters.description: The mileage program to retrieve availability from.

parameters.name: cabin
parameters.description: Only returns results with this cabin available. Must be one of: [economy, premium, business, first]

parameters.name: start_date
parameters.description: Only returns results between start_date and end_date when specified.

parameters.name: end_date
parameters.description: Only returns results between start_date and end_date when specified.

parameters.name: origin_region
parameters.description: Only returns results originating in this region when specified. Must be one of: [North America, South America, Africa, Asia, Europe, Oceania]

parameters.name: destination_region
parameters.description: Only returns results arriving in this region when specified. Must be one of: [North America, South America, Africa, Asia, Europe, Oceania]

parameters.name: take
parameters.description: How many results to return. Must be >=10 and <= 1000 if specified, otherwise 500.

parameters.name: cursor
parameters.description: Cursor you retrieved from a previous availability response.

parameters.name: skip
parameters.description: How many results to skip that you have already retrieved. Use this with the cursor to paginate responses.
